nk:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg>Download PDF</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2529442\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2529442\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Aug 06, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104kyx1665702979339.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/kyx1665702979339.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/kyx1665702979339.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"kyx1665702979339\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Syntax of Meta Characters\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"kyx1665702979339__syntax_of_meta_characters_179870\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">In keyboard translation tables, the characters in meta character sets can be mapped to a keystroke or combination of keystrokes.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"kyx1665702979339__topic_d62972e1_d62973e1_d62974e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kyx1665702979339__p_d62975e1_d62976e1_d62977e1\">{<var class=\"keyword varname\">FontNumber</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">.</code>}<var class=\"keyword varname\">Character</var>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kyx1665702979339__topic_d41522e1_d41523e1_d41524e1_d41525e1_d41526e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d892771e68\">\n                       \n Arguments\n </h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"kyx1665702979339__li_d27500e1_d27501e1_d27502e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">FontNumber</var>—optional; if omitted, the default is Font 0.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"kyx1665702979339__li_d27503e1_d27504e1_d27505e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Character</var>—literal character or its decimal value, for example <code class=\"ph codeph\">B</code> or <code class=\"ph codeph\">^66</code>.\n <p class=\"p\" id=\"kyx1665702979339__p_d62981e1_d62982e1_d62983e1\">For example, the positions <code class=\"ph codeph\">1.A</code> and <code class=\"ph codeph\">1.^065</code> are equivalent.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kyx1665702979339__topic_d41527e1_d41528e1_d41529e1_d41530e1_d41531e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d892771e104\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kyx1665702979339__p_d62987e1_d62988e1_d62989e1\">In keyboard translation tables, the characters in meta character sets can be mapped to a keystroke or combination of keystrokes.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kyx1665702979339__p_d62990e1_d62991e1_d62992e1\">For example, position <code class=\"ph codeph\">1.v</code> usually contains the <code class=\"ph codeph\">ö</code> character. To map the keystroke combination <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">PF1 v</span> on the VT100 keyboard to this character, you might use the following line in a VT100 keyboard definition:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">^ESC0Po 1.v</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kyx1665702979339__p_d62993e1_d62994e1_d62995e1\">However, this is not always obvious for the person using the keyboard. If you do provide the facility to map keystrokes to font characters, consider printing a keyboard layout chart for the end user, or provide help via the keyboard help mechanism.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/aud1665702670477.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Meta Character Sets</a><p>Meta character sets are used for translating installable character sets and defining translation tables. In earlier versions of Uniface, meta character sets were used as internal character sets instead of Unicode.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bhq1665702874003.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Defining Keyboard Help Text</a><p>The keyboard help function (^KEY_HELP) looks for its text in a global message which has the same name as the current value of $KEYBOARD in the current library and language.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529442\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529442\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Syntax of Meta Characters Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Aug 06, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Syntax of Meta Characters In keyboard translation tables, the characters in meta character sets can be mapped to a keystroke or combination of keystrokes. { FontNumber . } Character Arguments FontNumber —optional; if omitted, the default is Font 0. Character —literal character or its decimal value, for example B or ^66 . For example, the positions 1.A and 1.^065 are equivalent. Description In keyboard translation tables, the characters in meta character sets can be mapped to a keystroke or combination of keystrokes. For example, position 1.v usually contains the ö character. To map the keystroke combination PF1 v on the VT100 keyboard to this character, you might use the following line in a VT100 keyboard definition: ^ESC0Po 1.v Copy However, this is not always obvious for the person using the keyboard. If you do provide the facility to map keystrokes to font characters, consider printing a keyboard layout chart for the end user, or provide help via the keyboard help mechanism. Related Links Meta Character Sets Meta character sets are used for translating installable character sets and defining translation tables. In earlier versions of Uniface, meta character sets were used as internal character sets instead of Unicode. Defining Keyboard Help Text The keyboard help function (^KEY_HELP) looks for its text in a global message which has the same name as the current value of $KEYBOARD in the current library and language. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}